<ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT">The Harrisburg 7 trial</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">1972</ENAMEX> , in which <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Daniel Berrigan</ENAMEX> and others were charged with plotting anti-war - related violence , was a landmark .
